            {
                "comment": "Super casual, funny, and nice. One of my favorite teachers ever. I was in a 2 hour section but it never felt like more than 1. Very lenient on grading. I'm tempted to take another of his classes if possible even though I'm not really interested in pursuing Spanish.",
                "difficulty_rating": 2,
                "quality_rating": 5
